<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUH BOCHAN IN UM TUAH CH338</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nifate Jesuh min kha, Zum tuah, thli a hran tikah, Sifahnak tam
 hmanhsehlaw, Jesuh bochan in um tuah.

[C1]
   Nifate Bawipa Jesuh bochannak in va zum tuah, Baibal ca an cawnpiak
   bang, Jesuh bochan in um tuah.

[V2]
 Thiang Thlarau keimah chungah, A rung ceu ka lung chungah; Lam a ka
 hmuhsak zungzal, Jesuh bia lawng ka zumh lai.

[C2]
   Nifate Bawipa Jesuh bochannak in va zum tuah, Baibal ca an cawnpiak
   bang, Jesuh bochan in um tuah.

[V3]
 Lam nuamh lioah hla sa law, Khuamuih tikah thlacam tuah, Harnak ah
 Jesuh au tuah, Jesuh bochan in um tuah.

[C3]
   Nifate Bawipa Jesuh bochannak in va zum tuah, Baibal ca an cawnpiak
   bang, Jesuh bochan in um tuah.

[V4]
 Hi vawlei dih hnu tiangin, Amah ka zumh zungzal lai; Lungvar khua phak
 tik zongah, Bawi Jesuh lawng ka zumh lai.

[C4]
   Nifate Bawipa Jesuh bochannak in va zum tuah, Baibal ca an cawnpiak
   bang, Jesuh bochan in um tuah.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
<hymn_number>338</hymn_number>
</song>